description:
So many of us are here to connect with other people who can see through all the bullshit. People who aren’t scared. People who want their freedom back.

But some people are scared. Some people don’t care that the government is using the police to intimidate them into living small lives. What can you do?

Stay strong. Eat healthy. Exercise. And take a break from social media now and then. What use is being free if you’re constantly glued to the phone or computer saying “This is unbelievable? Why can’t everyone see what’s going on? When will this end?”

Go for a walk. Be free. You might make someone jealous.

In a good way.

Lots of love,

Ben
